{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0002", "text": "![State of TMT November 2018](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/media/netwerkkabels_538_tcm16-70945.jpg)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0002", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0003", "text": "The TMT sector continues to benefit from the favourable economic climate. Business confidence is high and entrepreneurs see few obstacles. A clear divide remains between strong and weak-performing segments.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0003", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0004", "text": "(Do you not see a download or are you unable to download the report? Then upgrade your browser to the most recent version.)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0004", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0005", "text": "1 MB](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/media/Stand-van-TMT-november-2018-1_tcm16-70941.pdf)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0005", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "The economic climate is favourable for the TMT sector, although economic growth is slowing. Economic indicators are less positive than earlier this year, but still at high levels. Despite the slowdown, the signals are still green for the TMT sector.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "Almost 55% of entrepreneurs in the sector say they do not face serious obstacles to growing their business. The obstacle that is often mentioned is the staff shortage. But at 29% this has fallen slightly compared with a quarter earlier.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0008", "text": "## IT and TV producers are the strongest growers. Telecoms, publishers and printers remain in the red", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0008", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0009", "text": "IT is by far the largest segment within the TMT sector and also the fastest-growing. IT will continue to grow strongly in the coming years. The segment of TV producers is performing better than expected and will see turnover rise by 5% this year. On the other hand, telecoms, publishers and printers continue to shrink.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0009", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0010", "text": "1 MB](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/media/Stand-van-TMT-november-2018-1_tcm16-70941.pdf)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0010", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0011", "text": "Technology, Media & Telecom (TMT) is one of the fastest-growing sectors. Helped by the increasing use of software, algorithms and sensors, this sector underpins the digital renewal of other sectors.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT november 2018__c4-paragraph__0011", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT november 2018", "source_title": "State of TMT November 2018", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
